page.title: 08LORRAINE'S DAY,FT.AUGUSTUS(2
page.content: We do project work until twenty to two,when we go to art.At fifteen minutes past two we stop art and go to music until two fifty five,when we get a ten minute interval.After that we go back to the classroom.Sometimes we get English or project work until about three forty five when our home work is given out.At four o'clock we go home. When I get home I put my coat and bag away.Then I get a few biscuits to eat then I sit down and watch the television for an hour. Then I do my home work.At six o'clock I have my tea, usually beefburgers and chips.Afterwards I go out until ten past eight when I come in to watch Dallas.After that I watch a film if there is a good one on .At about eleven or half past eleven I go up to my bed room and read in bed.
